  is '产品编号0900100100201-活期户 0900100100202-新活期户 0900500100204-P2P1.0 0900500100205-P2P2.0 0900500100206-P2B(对公户) 0900500100207-P2P3.0';
comment on column RRP_MDL.O_IOL_IFDS_BILL_FIN_ACC_ASSOC.account_role_type_id
